name: Ben's Finale
description: Finale has been the plan the whole time and will continue to be the plan. Finale is something that if you were paying attention to, you would’ve been on top of. It is an attention economy and attention is awarded. It is more than that too and to find out what else it is read between the lines. The Grand Finale is soon, please prepare yourself accordingly. Get ready for an experience unlike anything you’ve ever seen.
